node.text: Met my brother @___devonte___ in 7th grade open gym at Walker Mill middle school, we still rockin.....he created @enspirestreetwear a few years back and collabed with @nike on some KD13s....what a Fuckin honor it was to hoop in these...I know what my boy been through so I’m glad we could make this happen!!! Great win NETS WORLD
